---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Mainhero from "../components/mainhero.astro";
import Primary from "../components/primary.astro";
import Secondary from "../components/secondary.astro";
import Iconbar from "../components/iconbar.astro";
import Sustainable from "../components/sustainable.astro";
import ImgText from "../components/imagetext.astro";
import Newsletter from "../components/newslettersignup.astro";
import Blogsection from "../components/blogsection.astro";
import IconbarHome from "../components/iconbarHome.astro";
---
<Layout title="THE OATER">
    <Mainhero
        heroImage="oater-full.png"
        heroHeading="Press For Revolution"
        heroSubtitle="The Oater® Oat Drink Machine"
        heroText="The machine for fresh and sustainable oat drink with barista quality for professionals."
>

        <Primary slot="button" buttonName="to the waitlist" buttonUrl="https://share-eu1.hsforms.com/1KM3gGgfeS1mdqBzwXyDhbgfnkng" />
    </Mainhero>

    <ImgText title="Our Mission" imgUrl="/mission.jpg">
        Oat drink in a carton was yesterday. The Oater® machine produces the oat drink of the future. We are rethinking oat drink - with full
        barista quality and freshness – no packaging waste, no added sugar and no tradeoffs.
        <Secondary slot="button" buttonName="Our Mission" buttonUrl="/about" />
    </ImgText>

    <IconbarHome
        bgcolor="bg-oat-superlight"
        title="Oat Drink Without Tradeoffs"
        icontitle1="Fresh + Local"
        imgUrl1="/frischlokal.svg"
        icontitle2="Barista Quality"
        imgUrl2="/coffee.svg"
        icontitle3="Low-Waste"
        imgUrl3="/verpackungsarm.svg"
        icontitle4="Cost Saving"
        imgUrl4="/preiswert.svg"
        icontitle5="Without Added Sugar"
        imgUrl5="/zucker.svg"
    >
        <Secondary slot="button" buttonName="Our Solution" buttonUrl="/solution" />
    </IconbarHome>

    <ImgText title="The OATeam" imgUrl="/founders.webp" reverse>
        We are a team of dreamers and oat drink enthusiasts from Cologne, who firmly believe that there is still room for improvement in oat
        drink. It all started when our CEO Sarah, who has been vegan for 7 years, was bothered by all the packaging waste and the lack of
        freshness of her oat drink. There has to be a better way, she thought to herself. And now over 1 year later, we can say with
        conviction: Yes, it can be better! Our oat drink is fresher, more regional, cheaper, more delicious AND more sustainable than other
        solutions in the market today. We are
        <a
            href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/sarah-nesti"
            target="_blank"
            class="font-semibold text-oat-dark underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 duration-500 hover:text-oat hover:transition-all"
            >Sarah</a
        >, <a
            href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/henrikburger/en"
            target="_blank"
            class="font-semibold text-oat-dark underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 duration-500 hover:text-oat hover:transition-all"
            >Henrik</a
        >, <a
            href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/lisanesti/en"
            target="_blank"
            class="font-semibold text-oat-dark underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 duration-500 hover:text-oat hover:transition-all"
            >Lisa</a
        > and
        <a
            href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/benjamin-auer-68668a1a7/en"
            target="_blank"
            class="font-semibold text-oat-dark underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 duration-500 hover:text-oat hover:transition-all"
            >Benjamin</a
        > – <span class="font-semibold">Join our oat drink revolution!</span>
        <Secondary slot="button" buttonName="About Us" buttonUrl="/about" />
    </ImgText>

    <Sustainable
        background="bg-zinc-200"
        heading="Sustainability"
        subtitle="With The Oater®…"
        susData={[
            {
                iconUrl: "/kohlenstoffdioxid.svg",
                title: "…you reduce C02 emissions.",
                text: "Our ingredient packs weigh only 1/10 of a packaged oat drink. And less weight and organic oats from Germany means less transport emissions.",
            },
            {
                iconUrl: "/verpackung.svg",
                title: "…you save 100% packaging waste.",
                text: "Our oat drink comes without any disposable packaging at all, saving up to 100% packaging waste. We have developed a reusable packaging system for our ingredient mix.",
            },
            {
                iconUrl: "/klimaneutral.svg",
                title: "…you stay climate-neutral",
                text: "It’s important to us to produce as few emissions as possible in our entire value chain and we optimize continuously. The unavoidable emissions are compensated.",
            },
        ]}
    >
        <Secondary slot="button" buttonName="sustainability" buttonUrl="/sustainability" />
    </Sustainable>

    <Blogsection
        headline="Magazin"
        blogData={[
            {
                href: "https://magazin.oater.de/de/2022/10/19/mehr-nachhaltigkeit-im-cafe",
                imgUrl: "/sowirddeincafenachhaltiger.webp",
                tag: "sustainable",
                title: "So wird Dein Café nachhaltiger",
                author: "Sebastian",
                date: "Okt. 19, 2022",
            },
            {
                href: "https://magazin.oater.de/de/2022/07/07/das-ultimative-vegane-macaroni-and-cheese-rezept",
                imgUrl: "/macaroni.webp",
                tag: "REZEPT HUB",
                title: "DAS vegane Macaroni and Cheese Rezept",
                author: "Lisa",
                date: "Jul. 7, 2022",
            },
            {
                href: "https://magazin.oater.de/de/2022/08/02/tipps-gegen-lebensmittelverschwendung",
                imgUrl: "/retteretich.webp",
                tag: "ECO-FRIENDLY LIVING",
                title: "5 Tipps für weniger Lebensmittelverschwendung",
                author: "Katharina",
                date: "Aug. 2, 2022",
            },
        ]}
    >
        <Secondary slot="button" buttonName="Read more articles" buttonUrl="https://magazin.oater.de/de" />
    </Blogsection>
    <script type="text/javascript" id="hs-script-loader" async defer src="//js-eu1.hs-scripts.com/26294092.js"></script>
    <!-- Add a container div to wrap the button -->
    <div id="cookie_button_container">
        <!-- Add HubSpot Cookie trigger button HTML -->
        <button
            type="button"
            id="hs_show_banner_button"
            onClick="(function(){
                var _hsp = window._hsp = window._hsp || [];
                _hsp.push(['showBanner']);
            })()"
        >
            Cookie Settings
        </button>
    </div>

    <style>
        /* Add custom CSS for the container */
        #cookie_button_container {
            display: none; /* Hide the container by default */
        }

        /* Adjust the vertical position as needed, e.g., top: 30%; */
        #cookie_button_container.show-button {
            display: block; /* Show the container when it has the "show-button" class */
            position: fixed;
            right: 0;
            top: 21%; /* Set the initial vertical position to 30% */
            z-index: 999; /* Ensure it's above other content */
        }

        /* Add custom CSS for the HubSpot Cookie trigger button */
        #hs_show_banner_button {
            background-color: #ead18c;
            border: 1px solid #ead18c;
            border-radius: 3px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: inherit;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: inherit;
            text-align: left;
            text-shadow: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition:  0.3s; /* Add a smooth transition effect */
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        #hs_show_banner_button:hover {
            opacity: 1; /* Increase opacity on hover to 100% */
        }
    </style>

    <script>
        // JavaScript to show the button container after the Newsletter section
        window.addEventListener("scroll", function() {
            var newsletterSection = document.getElementById("newsletter_section");
            var buttonContainer = document.getElementById("cookie_button_container");

            if (newsletterSection && window.scrollY >= newsletterSection.offsetTop) {
                buttonContainer.classList.add("show-button");
            } else {
                buttonContainer.classList.remove("show-button");
            }
        });
    </script>
    <a id="newsletter_section"></a>
    <Newsletter headline="Join The OATeam">
        Sign up for the newsletter and learn immediately about new recipes and company news! And do not worry for our mails the same claim
        applies, as for our oat drink - no garbage.
    </Newsletter>
</Layout>
